{"tid":7104,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京 輕井澤 草津 七天遊","createTime":"2016-11-27T16:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T01:42:44.000Z","uid":18801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b677a886982e4f4454f707c2f726e818e72cf3f7","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"一月頭去東京<br />\n第一天 築地 銀座<br />\n第二天 台場<br />\n第三天 富士山 蘆之湖<br />\n第四天 迪士尼<br />\n第五天 輕井澤 滑雪<br />\n第六天 草津 溫泉<br />\n第七天 番機場<br />\n<br />\n想問下 富士山有咩活動？ 係咪得離遠睇？<br />\n輕井澤係咪冇咩好行？<br />\n草津溫泉係咪好多公眾 露天個種？<br />\n希望各位巴絲打比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4410103e2744334e41ae06a676897e420b85c98c","tid":7104,"uid":5036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"【重要】近既景點pack埋連日，盡量減少搬酒店。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cd3c1d28fb4f3ff052169306db05ef822824a9","tid":7104,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"輕井澤冬天得滑雪同outlet<br />\n舊銀座好多舖都唔開<br />\n草津好似得一個公眾露天風呂"},{"pid":"cccc3115be4e30642ca2446cfbbcd2a430f8cec8","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【重要】近既景點pack埋連日，盡量減少搬酒店。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係草津同輕井澤 係其中一個地方訓兩晚好d?"},{"pid":"14dbaf9291b704b1459f5f4d90a1d702fb5187fb","tid":7104,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:09:19.000Z","msg":"輕井澤留多晚"},{"pid":"eec58bbe789e6cbd2756c7f74bd02359c8f361a4","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕井澤留多晚</blockquote><br />\n除左滑雪 仲有咩活動？"},{"pid":"66eb2205b82fad372a2c6160ca2582f147f94532","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"如果係想滑雪 浸溫泉<br />\n除左箱根仲有冇咩選擇？<br />\n因為箱根個到冇酒店好住<br />\n加上草津好似正d"},{"pid":"6b6e453a368c3844d30366b669ef5554fa65f5ee","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"推兩推"},{"pid":"84a31dcf8f3e73fcf0d81d2cd5950c79494c6c4a","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"有冇都係去東京既巴打分享下行程"},{"pid":"0f284107b07dfc9dcc1505c50e1aba183d926699","tid":7104,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>輕井澤留多晚</blockquote><br />\n除左滑雪 仲有咩活動？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輕井澤都有溫泉<br />\n唔使特登去草津<br />\n係輕井澤嗰間酒店住一晚仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e99f6fae656d11482a722bc7375d8aa27064265","tid":7104,"uid":5036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"冬天既輕井澤除左滑雪真係無咩好做，舊輕井澤銀座通一帶又唔開，我唔建議留太長"},{"pid":"68953acd1964072a2b8e341f9dc360944498f9ff","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冬天既輕井澤除左滑雪真係無咩好做，舊輕井澤銀座通一帶又唔開，我唔建議留太長</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到 咁都係直去草津<br />\n除左草津 仲有冇邊到有滑雪溫泉一次過？"},{"pid":"83fe30c54bdda7cdfb5a5ea513e7cb48f7280215","tid":7104,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"去迪士尼晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左買迪士尼野唔建議去不過東京都有迪士尼商品鋪"},{"pid":"2d8a095bde387bcc7349a2247553a95a72ce333f","tid":7104,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去迪士尼晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左買迪士尼野唔建議去不過東京都有迪士尼商品鋪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留多一日黎行好過      一個機動遊戲排成個鐘"},{"pid":"c1092d168a98129cf1f67d6cef5892d26faee0b2","tid":7104,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"我個行程都幾似你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea314ab4768c4ff57adbdca1235383c7da3ba2d2","tid":7104,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去迪士尼晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左買迪士尼野唔建議去不過東京都有迪士尼商品鋪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留多一日黎行好過      一個機動遊戲排成個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本人同事表示香港嗰個仲好 啲嘢夠新淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話日本嗰邊俾人玩殘哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 兩邊未去過 得個聽字"},{"pid":"363c5c9318302b82bd142ebe3c9eb313bff05594","tid":7104,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"Day1 早機到 應該行陣買野之後夜晚倒數<br />\nDay2 河口湖<br />\nDay3 未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay4 輕井澤9遊住一晚<br />\nDay5 草津溫泉住一晚<br />\nDay6 野猿公苑附近住一晚<br />\nDay7 翻東京<br />\nDay8 翻香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我咁樣plan是咪好7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哂左一日搭翻東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d30a87522bd513ca38490781cb7afd0a1f6dc1","tid":7104,"uid":36798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:57:52.000Z","msg":"台場行outlet 有溫泉<br />\n可以search下 大江戶 既溫泉<br />\n勁多人 好有特色"},{"pid":"8cfa19729d149b3f7f762fee717e4754eac72ac1","tid":7104,"uid":3555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"我之前係去台場個溫泉 不過唔係溫泉酒店 未必有位你瞓"},{"pid":"bb48574082bf139944e76b578396a648179300b8","tid":7104,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"有無人浸過輕井澤個星野溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔鍾意多人 不考慮大江户<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b631ac923c409a53d6b8cca6a75f6fd88c6c12","tid":7104,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人浸過輕井澤個星野溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔鍾意多人 不考慮大江户<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輕井澤住過Cypress Hotel，正到顛"},{"pid":"3525034487bc5268359926c3803185f64179a52d","tid":7104,"uid":36990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:50:29.000Z","msg":"唔反對去迪士尼，但建議去海個邊"},{"pid":"2a01edc1456cf1f87c1a877086748d55e4e03ea2","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去迪士尼晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左買迪士尼野唔建議去不過東京都有迪士尼商品鋪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留多一日黎行好過      一個機動遊戲排成個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你星期幾去？<br />\n我星期一去。希望少人d掛<br />\n如果真係多人 會買fast pass"},{"pid":"555b18aeaec384c9be8b8eec76c20249bae08426","tid":7104,"uid":18801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打可以分享下 富士山 蘆之湖既行程<br />\n我見好多人 都淨係講覽車"},{"pid":"04acdd46bcfe86845fc1b6de5a55f169be7c3429","tid":7104,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去迪士尼晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左買迪士尼野唔建議去不過東京都有迪士尼商品鋪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留多一日黎行好過      一個機動遊戲排成個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你星期幾去？<br />\n我星期一去。希望少人d掛<br />\n如果真係多人 會買fast pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我記得得唔係星期六日去都好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}